{
  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of Yosemite Valley, featuring towering granite cliffs on either side. El Capitan is prominently visible on the left, while Half Dome stands majestically in the distance. A cascading waterfall plummets down from a high cliff face, creating a misty veil. The valley floor is densely covered with a lush green forest, creating a vibrant contrast with the gray and brown rock formations. Above, a cloudy sky adds a dynamic element to the scene. Patches of snow remain visible on the upper peaks, hinting at higher elevations and cooler temperatures.",
